 the Pagani Huayra Codalunga Speedster can be equipped with a seven-speed, gated manual transmission. What a beautiful thing that shifter is–a perfect example of the obsessive attention to detail you’ll find in every single Pagani masterpiece. With every shift, your eardrums will be soothed with the serene sounds of the AMG-constructed V12, vibrantly echoed through a titanium six-way exhaust system which, according to Pagani, “reduces weight and provides an unmistakable sound signature, a defining hallmark of every Pagani creation.” Yeah, Pagani knows exactly what they’re doing to us with this one.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Pagani Huayra Codalunga Speedster\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTgz/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_01-01.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"old-school-elegance-contemporary-construction\"\u003eOld-school elegance, contemporary construction\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eDespite its styling, which is evocative of 1950s and ’60s racing cars, the Pagani Huayra Codalunga Speedster is much more advanced under the surface than one might expect. The Speedster’s Carbo-Titanium and Carbo-Triax monocoque “ensures rigidity and lightness,” while its active suspension system, Brembo-developed carbon-ceramic brakes made specifically for Pagani, and Pirelli Trofeo R tires allow for incredibly precise and intuitive handling.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Pagani Huayra Codalunga Speedster\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTYx/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_int8_srgb.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"bespoke-to-its-very-core\"\u003eBespoke to its very core\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003eAs Pagani puts it, “the Huayra Codalunga Speedster is born from listening.” Each of the ten individual Codalunga Speedsters that will be produced will take shape “through a direct dialogue with each client, with no limits to vision or desire,” allowing for personalization to an intimate and extreme degree. The ability to specify your very own Codalunga Speedster to your heart’s content is endless, so long as you’ve got the required funds and a strong relationship with Pagani to see it through.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"Pagani Huayra Codalunga Speedster\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" sizes=\"(min-width: 750px) 750px, calc(100vw - 60px)\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 1200w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1920,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 1920w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_2048,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 2048w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg 3840w\" src=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_3840,q_auto:good,c_limit/NzowMDAwMDAwMDAwOTE5NTc1/pagani-huayra-codalunga-speedster_05-02.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"final-thoughts\"\u003eFinal thoughts\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp data-wp-block=\"{\u0026#34;dropCap\u0026#34;:false}\" data-wp-block-name=\"core/paragraph\"\u003ePerhaps the ultimate expression of automotive excellence, Pagani’s latest vehicular virtuoso, the Huayra Codalunga Speedster, is truly unlike any other motor vehicle money could possibly buy. Its uniqueness is truly unmatched, and it’s equally as deserving of a spot on an art museum plinth as a Michelangelo sculpture. This is a vehicle that already looks like it’s conquered the test of time, and with its breathtaking styling and robust AMG-sourced power plant, it should age just as gracefully as a fine Barolo wine. More like this, please, Pagani.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003eAbout the Author\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"fill\" sizes=\"100px\" srcset=\"https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_16,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 16w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_32,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 32w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_48,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 48w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_64,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 64w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_96,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 96w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_128,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 128w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_256,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 256w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_384,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 384w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_640,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 640w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_750,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 750w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_828,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 828w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1080,q_auto:good,c_fill,ar_1:1/MjEyMzUwMDg4NjE2MzU1NDU2/cole-attisha.jpg 1080w, https://www.autoblog.com/.image/w_1200,q_auto:g